Who knew Burgers could do so much good? @billykramer, founder of @nfaburger, one of the highest rated Burgers in Atlanta, just raised $50,000 for @GivingKitchen!

Giving Kitchen provides emergency assistance for food service workers through financial support and a network of community resources.

Billy brought a ridiculously talented and creative group of restaurateurs and Chefs together to smash Burgers in a parking lot.

Each Chef or restaurant had to make their version of the Well-Made Cheeseburger from @themenufilm.

It was a pleasure and an honor to be a part of such a great event working some incredibly talented folks to put some good into the world.

Here’s a photo dump of each one the Burgers from the event.

